@node Main "Quetiles - Documentation"

                              Quetiles 1.04

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Quetiles' is a @{" game " link play} where your goal is to change all the tiles
so that they are all the same colour. It may sound simple, but there's
a catch: as you change a tile, one or two other tiles will also change
their colour.

  Each game board uses 5 different colours and these colours will
change following a certain order (for example: red-blue-green-white-
yellow-red...) but the tiles affected by the one you changed will
change their colour in the opposite order (yellow-white-green-blue-
red...).

  Have fun!

