@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place Quetiles where you want on
your system (hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc.). No other files
or Libraries are needed. The only requirement is that your Workbench must
have at least 8 colours.

                             How to play?

  To change the colour of a tile, just click on it, the colour of
the 'linked' tiles will also change.

  Note that you can choose any colour for the tiles, in fact the
colour used for the tiles isn't important. What is important is that
@{b}all@{ub} the tiles must be of the same colour in order to complete the game.
 
  The 'linked' tiles will remain the same for each game. This means
that each time you click on one of the tiles to change its colour, the
same linked tiles will change their colour.

  Have fun!

OPTIONS

  In the game window, there are 3 buttons:

 -@{b}New Game@{ub}:                Restarts the game.

 -@{b}About...@{ub}:                Displays the informations about the game.

 -@{b}5 by 5...11 by 11 Board@{ub}: To choose between the different game boards.

